Bring the glass to the sink.
Put the glass on the edge of the sink.

place the cup inside the fridge, wait, then take it back out
place the cup in the sink

high_descs: Pick up the clear glass next to the coffee maker.
Turn around and head towards the fridge on your right.
Put the glass cup in the fridge for it to cool and then take it out of the fridge.
Turn left and head towards the sink.
Place the glass cup in front of the spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled glass cup in the sink.
